ğŸ§± STRUCTURE OF A WELL-WRITTEN FINDING
Each finding should include:

Component	What to Include	Pro Tip for Exam
Title	Concise, clear vulnerability or issue name. E.g., Weak Kerberos Authentication (Kerberoasting)	Use standard terminology
Description	Detailed explanation of what the issue is and what systems it affects	Teach the reader (assume theyâ€™ve never heard of it)
